title: VideoMach 5.10.5 + Serial
description:
VideoMach is a powerful media converter that supports video  video, image  image and audio  audio conversions, with all possible variations. Use it to create videos from images, add music to animations, decompile movies to images and audio, resize / crop / rotate / speed up / slow down and apply numerous effects to videos and images.

VideoMach opens large image sequences faster than any other software (as long the the right procedure is being followed) and supports exotic file formats found in high-speed imagers. For that reason VideoMach is the application of choice by professionals and enthusiasts that create videos out of images produced by 3D renderers, high-speed imagers, stop-motion animation and time-lapse cameras.
